    39→### Key Characteristics
    40→
    41→| Property | Value |
    42→|----------|-------|
    43→| Transport | WebSocket (`ws://` or `wss://`) |
    44→| Protocol | NDJSON (one JSON object per `\n`-terminated line) |
    45→| Direction | CLI connects TO your server (CLI = client) |
    46→| Auth | `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header on upgrade |
    47→| First message | Server sends `user` message, CLI responds with `system/init` |
