   290→### 6.3. `assistant` — LLM Response (CLI → Server)
   291→
   292→Full assistant message after LLM completes a response.
   293→
   294→```typescript
   295→interface SDKAssistantMessage {
   296→  type: "assistant";
   297→  message: {
